e family_lato"><div id="header" class="header has_image align_center"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyMTcwNDY4LnBuZw==/original/u0QRR5.png" alt="Satiety"/><h1 itemprop="name" class="game_title">Satiety</h1></div><div id="view_html_game_9028004" class="view_html_game_page view_game_page page_widget base_widget buy_on_top ready"><div id="html_embed_7514343" class="html_embed_widget base_widget embed_wrapper"><div data-height="360" data-width="640" class="game_frame game_pending start_maximized" style="width: 640px; height: 360px"><div class="restore_wrapper"><button class="restore_btn button"><svg stroke-linejoin="round" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" role="img" stroke-width="2" class="svgicon icon_play" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden version="1.1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Restore game</button></div><div class="iframe_placeholder" data-iframe="&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://v6p9d9t4.ssl.hwcdn.net/html/7912210/Satiety/index.html&quot; allowtransparency=&quot;true&quot; webkitallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; mozallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; msallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; allow=&quot;autoplay; fullscreen *; geolocation; microphone; camera; midi; monetization; xr-spatial-tracking; gamepad; gyroscope; accelerometer; xr; cross-origin-isolated&quot; id=&quot;game_drop&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"><button class="button load_iframe_btn"><svg stroke-linejoin="round" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" role="img" stroke-width="2" class="svgicon icon_play" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden version="1.1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Run game</button></div></div></div><div class="donate"><a href="https://mikeleeten.itch.io/satiety/purchase" class="button donate_btn" data-donate="false">Download Now</a></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><p><em>Highly recommended to download the Windows game build for better performance.&nbsp;</em></p>  <p><em>Donation is not necessary to play the game, but definitely much appreciated for me to keep making games.</em></p>  <p>---</p>  <h2>SATIETY</h2>  <p>This is a short escape room style&nbsp;horror game about you trying to escape and figure out what happened to you. The game play length is only about 5 to 10 minutes.</p>  <p>Find objects, read notes and figure out puzzles to get out of this eerie room.</p>  <p>---</p>  <p><strong>#SYNTYGameJam</strong><br></p>  <p>---</p>  <p>This game is created as part of the Synty game jam submission for the theme <strong>&quot;Wait, Are We The Bad Guys?&quot;</strong></p>  <p>The game might feel incomplete as it was created within 3 weeks and a lot of features has not been implemented yet, but it shouldn&#x27;t deter you from the game experience.</p>  <p>Your comments and feedbacks are very much appreciated as I might be updating this game after the Jam.</p>  <p>---</p>  <h2>BASIC CONTROLS</h2>  <p>Only support keyboard and mouse.  </p>  <p>W,A,S,D - Walk  </p>  <p>LEFT SHIFT - Sprint  </p>  <p>F - Interact  </p>  <p>T - Flashlight  </p>  <p>C - Crouch  </p>  <p>Tab - Back / Pause</p>  <p>---<br></p>  <p><strong>If you enjoy my game, you can support me by wishlisting my upcoming horror game &quot;The Guestlist&quot; here:<br></strong><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2354840/The_Guestlist/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong></strong></a><strong><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2354840/The_Guestlist/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://store.steampowered.com/app/2354840/The_Guestlist/</a></strong><span></span></p>  <p><strong>Or you can follow my development on Twitter&nbsp;:&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://twitter.com/Mi